# Google OAuth client secret for the Drive backend, injected at build time.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (which is gitignored) and paste the client secret from
# the Google Cloud Console → APIs & Services → Credentials → the Konode OAuth 2.0
# "Web application" client. Official Konode builds set this so the Drive backend
# works out of the box.
#
# Leave it empty for a source build: the Drive backend then sends no secret and
# would need your own OAuth client to work. GitHub and WebDAV need nothing here.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=
